</div>

<div class="container-fluid" style="border: 0px; background-color: lightgrey">
  <div class = "row-fluid" style="background-color: #lightgrey">
    <div class = "well-large">
    <h3 class="lead">Automated Microscopy, Lab Automation and Robotics</h3>

    <div class = "row" style="background-color: #lightgrey">
      <img src="lab_photos/03_Robot.jpg" class = "col-3">
      <p class="col-9">We use custom software and hardware to automate our microscopes and microfluidic chips to perform tedious pipetting and imaging tasks efficiently. We automate cell loading, cell feeding, stimulation and time-lapse imaging steps to save us time and manpower. We also have access to the pipetting robot and the lab automation facility at the D-BSSE for large scale screens and cloning.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class = "row-fluid" style="background-image:url('billie_holiday.png')">
  <div class="span12"></div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid" style="border: 0px; background-color: lightgrey">
  <div class = "row-fluid" style="background-color: #lightgrey">
    <div class = "well-large">
    <h3 class="lead">Fluorescence/Confocal Microscopy</h3>

    <div class = "row" style="background-color: #lightgrey">
      <img src="lab_photos/01_Confocal.jpg" class = "col-3">
      <p class="col-9">We have automated wide-field fluorescence microscopy capabilities in our lab that is used for live-cell imaging and quantification of cells and proteins. We also have access to the state-of-the-art cell culture grade confocal microscopy systems and the single-cell facility (We are currently integrating microfluidics and automation to these systems)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class = "row-fluid" style="background-image:url('billie_holiday.png')">
  <div class="span12"></div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid" style="border: 0px; background-color: lightgrey">
  <div class = "row-fluid" style="background-color: #lightgrey">
    <div class = "well-large">
    <h3 class="lead">Deep Sequencing/RNA sequencing</h3>

    <div class = "row" style="background-color: #lightgrey">
      <img src="lab_photos/06_Illumina.jpg" class = "col-3">
      <p class="col-9">e have access to deep seequencing/RNA sequencing (Illumina) at the D-BSSE genomics facility. We plan to use RNA-sequencing for large-scale gene expression screens and combine it with the microfluidic capabilities of the Fluidigm Biomark q-PCR, cell sorting and microfluidic cell culture and single-cell analysis.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class = "row-fluid" style="background-image:url('billie_holiday.png')">
  <div class="span12"></div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid" style="border: 0px; background-color: lightgrey">
  <div class = "row-fluid" style="background-color: #lightgrey">
    <div class = "well-large">
    <h3 class="lead">Stochastic/Deterministic Modeling of Signaling Pathway Dynamics</h3>

    <div class = "row-fluid" style="background-color: #lightgrey">
      <p class="span12">We have previously developed stochastic and deterministic models of the NF-kappaB pathway. We will continue to use this modeling strategy and combine it with quantitative, high-througput experimental data to improve the accuracy and scope of our models. Our models, in return, improve our understanding of the underlying biological mechanisms, develop insight and guide our experimental studies. We also collaborate with Tomasz Lipniacki (Polish Academy of Sciences), Dagmar Iber (D-BSSE, ETH Zurich) and other computational groups at D-BSSE.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class = "row-fluid" style="background-image:url('billie_holiday.png')">
  <div class="span12"></div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid" style="border: 0px; background-color: lightgrey">
