    <h3 class="lead">Automated Single Cell Tracking and Data Analysis</h3>

    <div class = "row-fluid" style="background-color: #lightgrey">
      <p class="span12">We use fluorescent nuclear markers and custom software to track cells in real-time as they move in 2D microfluidic surfaces, and extract intensity levels from cytoplasm and nucleus to account for protein activity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
